<table cellpadding=3D"20">
<tbody><tr><td><h7><b>Properties of the Dodecahedron</b></h7></td></tr>
<tr><td><li>Faces: 12 pentagons</li><li>Vertices: 20, each with 3 edges mee=
ting
  </li><li>Edges: 30</li><li>Dihedral angle: 116=B034'</li></td></tr>

<tr><td><h7><b>The Symmetry</b></h7></td></tr>
<tr><td><a href=3D"https://personal.math.ubc.ca/~cass/courses/m308/projects=
